  "title": "Class 4 Driver",
  "description": "<p><strong>* Monday to Saturday, 8am - 5pm</strong><br /><strong>* Location: Bedok</strong><br /><strong>* Class 4 license is a must</strong><br /><strong>* Basic + OT + Bonus</strong><br /><strong>* High gross salary with OT pay</strong><br /><strong>* Permanent role</strong></p><p><strong>Our client is a leading food supply solutions and services provider</strong><br /></p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><p><ul><li>Deliver food products to clients in a timely and safe manner</li><li>Load and unload food items in accordance with food hygiene and safety standards</li><li>Ensure proper handling of food products, including cold-chain requirements where applicable</li><li>Maintain cleanliness and basic maintenance of the assigned company vehicle</li><li>Complete delivery documentation, logs and reports accurately</li><li>Comply with traffic regulations, food safety requirements and company standard operating procedures (SOPs)</li></ul></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p><p><p><ul><li>Valid Class 4 driving licence</li><li>Physically fit and able to perform manual handling tasks such as loading and unloading</li><li>Able to perform the physical duties of the role, including reaching and stacking items at designated heights and handling goods safely in accordance with workplace safety requirements</li><li>Familiar with Singapore road networks</li></ul></p></p></p><p>HOW TO APPLY:</p><p>Interested applicants, please click on “Apply Now” or email to submit your resume.</p><p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be notified.<br /></p><p>Stafflink Services Pte Ltd</p><p>EA Licence No.: 04C4294</p><p>EA Personnel: Jason Bong Wee Kiat</p><p>EA Personnel Reg. No.: R23116067</p>",
